{"tid":1737481,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[極重要：被捕者家人朋友詳細須知] 推到上熱門","createTime":"2019-11-19T03:30:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T05:28:07.000Z","uid":182994,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"43383cd63789525e79629917965586de220cdd50","tid":1737481,"uid":182994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:30:07.000Z","msg":"呢條link係被捕者家人須知 <a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.thenewslens.com/amparticle/127614\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.thenewslens.com%2Famparticle%2F127614&d=uyJPOiOY0yV7leae1MMhfP3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=d6f8f732\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.thenewslens.com/amparticle/127614</a><br />\n<br />\n務必要睇，暴動罪最高刑罰係十年，請細心閱讀以上須知。<br />\n<br />\n被捕者朋友同家人請兵分兩路，一批去警署搵，一批要係屋企清野，每一樣相關既野都係證據，一定要清理好，同時要想辦法處理被捕者既社交媒體，最好暫時刪除。切記，就算幾緊張都好，唔好同警察講任何野，警察會扮好人問屋企人攞料。家人同朋友要保持頭腦清醒，先可以幫到小朋友。<br />\n<br />\n清屋企既野同唔好同警察講任何野係重中之重。"},{"pid":"fc53b87d47213fc2ed6b011b8a2450aacae66045","tid":1737481,"uid":237300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:34:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"052ec3202329193ac932387fc0276740d81253b9","tid":1737481,"uid":124636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:34:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c48969d8622b7a3b85b291c40ecbde0f774f623e","tid":1737481,"uid":182994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:53:59.000Z","msg":"推 有用post"},{"pid":"f7d579b98f0ff2c76d2420a81ac9db43c0ba28e5","tid":1737481,"uid":144084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:55:29.000Z","msg":"星期日前主線任 - 絕殺保皇黨!<br />\n支線任 - 檢討而不分化<br />\n幫推 : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1737525\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1737525</a>"},{"pid":"89acc37cbbc3945264a38cea7e82c61b06770576","tid":1737481,"uid":144084,"like":0,"d